short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Export business data from Google Maps to a CSV file.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Google Maps Business Exporter is a simple and efficient tool that helps you capture and export business information directly from Google Maps. With just a few clicks, you can save the name, address, and phone number of selected businesses into a CSV file for easy reference and organization.
